rock on brother !
been COLD here [NY] but not too much snow this year

On Wild Horses, Warren has Grace Potter singing with him - up until then I'd not heard of her.  This sort of discovery is one of the things I love about torrents. It wasn't until I heard Warren Haynes being thanked on someone or others cd years ago that I followed up on him and found this wealth of music he's contributed to.

TPB has two or three offerings from Grace Potter & the Nocturnals.  I'm listening to one now and I certainly haven't made a mistake getting it.  Thanks, once again for your work doing all this smb.

A post script is that this concert took place a week after the Haiti earthquake. Jamaica is relatively close to Haiti, so I would think there would have been quite a few thinking of that place?
I've seen Grace with both the Black Crowes and with Gov't Mule and they have put on a great show both times !!!!! what a voice !!!!
do a YTube search for GRACE POTTER MYSTERY TRAIN - freakin' killer performance !!!!!
